review_blob: They make this beer close to where I live.  Ive driven by the brewery hundreds of times but only recently decided to give it a try.  This is some of the best tasting beer Ive ever had, and I usually prefer dark beers.  Whenever I see this offered in town now, I always get a glass.
I used to drink guinees until I found Waterloo Dark, now this is my preferred brew.  Made in Waterloo Ontario Canada, and the stubby bottles are pretty cool too!
